<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>MyRead - Home</title>
		<style>
body {
	background-color: #191919;
	color: #D9D9D9;
}
h1, h2, h3, h4, h5 {
	color: #D93F3F;
}
input[type=text], input[type=password] {
	background-color: #D93F3F;
	color: #191919;
	padding: 12px 12px;
	border: none;
	outline: none;
}
input[type=submit] {
	background-color: #D93F3F;
	color: #191919;
	padding: 12px 24px;
	border: none;
	outline: none;
}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>MyRead - Home</h1>
		<% if session[:id] %>
		<p>Looks like meat's back on the menu, <%= session[:id] %>!</p>
	<% else %>
		<p>“You cannot pass,” he said. The orcs stood still, and a dead silence fell. “I am a servant of the Secret Fire, wielder of the flame of Anor. You cannot pass. The dark fire will not avail you, flame of Udûn. Go back to the Shadow! You cannot pass.”</p>
	<% end %>

		<h2>Login</h2>
		<form method="post" action="/login">
			<label for="name">Name:</label>
			<input id="name" name="name" type="text"></input>
			<label for="pass">Password:</label>
			<input id="pass" name="pass" type="password"></input>
			<input type="submit" value="Login"></input>
		</form>

		<h2>Register</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Minimum 9 characters, maximum 64</li>
			<li>Minimum 1 English uppercase + lowercase letter</li>
			<li>Minimum 1 digit</li>
			<li>Minimum 1 of these special characters - @$!%*?&</li>
			<li>Must not include username</li>
		</ul>
		<form method="post" action="/register">
			<label for="name">Name:</label>
			<input id="name" name="name" type="text"></input>
			<label for="pass">Password:</label>
			<input id="pass" name="pass" type="password"></input>
			<input type="submit" value="Register"></input>
		</form>

		<% if session[:id] %>
		<h2>Sign out</h2>
		<form method="get" action="/signout">
			<input type="submit" value="Sign out"></input>
		</form>
	<% end %>

	</body>
</html>
